# 根目錄 .env.example — 說明所有環境變數
# 前端請複製至 frontend/.env
# 後端請複製至 backend/local.settings.json

# ===== 前端 =====
REACT_APP_AZURE_CLIENT_ID=
REACT_APP_AZURE_TENANT_ID=common
REACT_APP_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
REACT_APP_GITHUB_CLIENT_ID=
REACT_APP_BACKEND_URL=

# ===== 後端 =====
AZURE_OPENAI_ENDPOINT=
AZURE_OPENAI_KEY=
AZURE_OPENAI_DEPLOYMENT=gpt-4
SPEECH_KEY=
SPEECH_REGION=eastasia
COSMOS_ENDPOINT=
COSMOS_KEY=
COSMOS_DATABASE=lisbot
STORAGE_ACCOUNT=
STORAGE_CONTAINER=audio-recordings
AZURE_STORAGE_CONNECTION_STRING=DefaultEndpointsProtocol=https;AccountName=...;AccountKey=...;EndpointSuffix=core.windows.net
WEB_PUBSUB_ENDPOINT=
WEB_PUBSUB_KEY=
WEB_PUBSUB_HUB=speech_hub
JWT_SECRET=
MICROSOFT_CLIENT_ID=
MICROSOFT_CLIENT_SECRET=
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=
GITHUB_CLIENT_ID=
GITHUB_CLIENT_SECRET=
APPLE_TEAM_ID=
APPLE_KEY_ID=
APPLE_CLIENT_ID=
APPLE_PRIVATE_KEY=
FRONTEND_URL=

# ===== GitHub Actions Secrets（請在 repo Settings > Secrets 設定）=====
# AZURE_STATIC_WEB_APPS_API_TOKEN  — Terraform output: frontend_deployment_token
# AZURE_CREDENTIALS                — az ad sp create-for-rbac 輸出
# AZURE_FUNCTION_APP_NAME          — Terraform output: func-lisbot-xxxxx
# REACT_APP_AZURE_CLIENT_ID        — 同上
# REACT_APP_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID       — 同上
# REACT_APP_GITHUB_CLIENT_ID       — 同上
# REACT_APP_BACKEND_URL            — Terraform output: backend_url
